```julia
julia> using BenchmarkTools

julia> x = 1; y = 2:2;

julia> @btime vcat($x, $x);
  33.696 ns (1 allocation: 80 bytes)

julia> @btime vcat($y, $y);
  40.178 ns (1 allocation: 80 bytes)

julia> @btime vcat($x, $y);
  43.897 ns (1 allocation: 80 bytes)
```

